          "process_md": "**Step 1:** The successor of the deceased or disabled farmer must submit an application within 150 days of the accident.\n**Step 2:** The application must be submitted to the concerned [District Agriculture Officer](https://dag.gujarat.gov.in/Home/FieldOffice).\n&gt; **Contact Us:** [Click here](https://dag.gujarat.gov.in/Home/FieldOffice).\n\n"
